Title: Georg Fischer Aquasystem saddle with spigot 90 x 32mm
Description: This Georg Fischer Aquasystem 90 x 32mm saddle with spigot (G-type) is part of a light, economical and corrosion-free polypropylene-random piping system. Suitable for commercial use, it can be used for riser and distribution runs in heating, domestic hot water, mains cold water and chilled water services.

Title: TP RB0.QRL abs serrated stub flange 4"
Description: This TP RB0.QRL 4 x 4" serrated face stub flange is made of high impact, highly elastic ABS and includes a stainless steel A2 reinforcing ring and plain/BSP threaded connection. Pressure ratings for thermoplastic pipe and fittings carrying water are quoted at 20°C and where the temperature increases, the working pressure must be reduced. ABS is resistant to most diluted inorganic acids, bases and salts and most animal oils and fats.

Title: Georg Fischer UPVC stub flange 3"
